{"word":"Dew","slug":"dew","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dew</b> A merciful providence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=13'>Deu 33:13</a><br/> Forms imperceptibly<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=12'>2Sa 17:12</a><br/> Forms in the night<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=29&verse=19'>Job 29:19</a><br/> From the clouds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=3&verse=20'>Pro 3:20</a><br/> Called the dew of heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=15'>Dan 4:15</a><br/> Absence of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ki 17:1</a><br/> Miraculous profusion and absence of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=40'>Jdg 6:40</a><br/><a href='S:Meteorology and Celestial Phenomena'>Meteorology and Celestial Phenomena</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=110&verse=3'>Psa 110:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=26&verse=19'>Isa 26:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=6&verse=4'>Hos 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=3'>Hos 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=14&verse=5'>Hos 14:5</a>"}]}